      <title>中国人民银行发出警告后，中国各银行维持贷款利率不变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/chinese-banks-hold-key-lending-rates-after-pboc-signals-caution</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于利润率面临压力且政策制定者关注金融机构的健康状况，中国各银行8月份维持基准贷款利率不变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/chinese-banks-hold-key-lending-rates-after-pboc-signals-caution</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 01:01:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
